        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 10px;"><strong>9:30 AM - 5:00 PM</strong></td>
            <td style="padding: 10px;">Team Execution</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px;">Team members work on tasks from daily plans</td>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <h2 id="troubleshooting">6. Troubleshooting Guide</h2>
    
    <h3>Common Issues & Solutions</h3>

    <div style="background: #fff3cd; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 15px 0; border-left: 4px solid #f0ad4e;">
        <h4>❌ Agent Doesn't Respond or Takes Too Long</h4>
        <p><strong>Cause:</strong> Zencoder experiencing lag or overload</p>
        <p><strong>Solution:</strong></p>
        <ol>
            <li>Wait 2-3 minutes; agent may still be processing</li>
            <li>Check network connection</li>
            <li>If >5 minutes, refresh browser (don't close chat)</li>
            <li>If still stuck, close chat and try prompt again in new chat</li>
            <li>If problem persists: Skip that agent, continue with next (not ideal but workflow continues)</li>
        </ol>
    </div>

    <div style="background: #f8d7da; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 15px 0; border-left: 4px solid #dc3545;">
        <h4>❌ Agent Says "Cannot Find File"</h4>
        <p><strong>Cause:</strong> File path is incorrect or file doesn't exist yet</p>
        <p><strong>Solution:</strong></p>
        <ol>
            <li>Check file location: <strong>/Comserv/root/Documentation/session_history/</strong> for audit files</li>
            <li>Verify date format in filename: YYYY-MM-DD (e.g., 2026-01-02.md)</li>
            <li>If Agent 1 hasn't run yet, audit file won't exist—run Agent 1 first</li>
            <li>Manually create audit file with placeholder content (ask tech lead)</li>
        </ol>
    </div>

    <div style="background: #d1ecf1; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 15px 0; border-left: 4px solid #17a2b8;">
        <h4>❌ /chathandoff Didn't Execute (Agent Didn't Move to Next Step)</h4>
        <p><strong>Cause:</strong> Agent completed work but forgot final checkpoint</p>
        <p><strong>Solution:</strong></p>
        <ol>
            <li>Type in chat: <strong>/chathandoff</strong> (manually execute checkpoint)</li>
            <li>Copy agent's output to session history manually (ask tech lead)</li>
            <li>Proceed to next agent in new chat</li>
            <li>Report to tech lead: "Agent 2 skipped /chathandoff"</li>
        </ol>
    </div>

    <div style="background: #d4edda; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 15px 0; border-left: 4px solid #28a745;">
        <h4>⚠️ Agent Made Unexpected Changes to Files</h4>
        <p><strong>Cause:</strong> Agent interpreted prompt incorrectly or had stale data</p>
        <p><strong>Solution:</strong></p>
        <ol>
            <li>Review changes in Git: <strong>git diff</strong> to see what changed</li>
            <li>If changes are correct: commit them with message "Auto-update from [Agent Name]"</li>
            <li>If changes are wrong: <strong>git checkout [filename]</strong> to revert</li>
            <li>Report issue to tech lead with details of what went wrong</li>
        </ol>
    </div>

    <h2 id="best-practices">7. Best Practices & Tips</h2>
    
    <div style="background: #e8f4f8; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px;">
        <h4>✅ Do This</h4>
        <ul style="line-height: 1.8;">
            <li><strong>Run workflow consistently:</strong> Same time each morning ensures predictable behavior</li>
            <li><strong>Keep prompts clear:</strong> Provide specific dates, file names, and context</li>
            <li><strong>Review outputs:</strong> Check generated files for accuracy before team uses them</li>
            <li><strong>Wait for /chathandoff:</strong> Don't start next chat until agent signals completion</li>
            <li><strong>Document issues:</strong> Log problems with agents for pattern analysis</li>
            <li><strong>Backup daily plans:</strong> If generating fails, use previous day as template</li>
            <li><strong>Communicate with team:</strong> Share daily plans as soon as Agent 4 completes</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div style="background: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; margin-top: 20px;">
        <h4>❌ Don't Do This</h4>
        <ul style="line-height: 1.8;">
            <li><strong>Skip agents:</strong> All 4 agents must run in sequence for workflow integrity</li>
            <li><strong>Reuse old chats:</strong> Always start fresh chats (old chats have stale context)</li>
            <li><strong>Edit agent prompts:</strong> Use templates as-is; only change [PLACEHOLDERS]</li>
            <li><strong>Run agents out of order:</strong> Agent 1 → 2 → 3 → 4 (no jumping)</li>
            <li><strong>Manually edit master plan:</strong> Let Agent 3 update it; manual edits cause version conflicts</li>
            <li><strong>Ignore errors:</strong> Report all issues to tech lead for troubleshooting</li>
            <li><strong>Keep old daily plans:</strong> Delete plans older than 14 days to save space</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

